---
import BaseHead from "~/components/BaseHead.astro";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="Scroll Sandwich Layout" description="A clean CSS Grid pattern for creating scrollable layouts with fixed headers and footers" />
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="scroll-sandwich">
			<header class="header">
				<p>header</p>
			</header>

			<div class="scroll-area scroll-fog">
				<div class="content">
					<h2>Scrollable Content Area</h2>
					<p>This area scrolls independently while the header and footer remain fixed.</p>
					
					<section>
						<h3>How it works</h3>
						<p>The layout uses CSS Grid with three rows:</p>
						<ul>
							<li><code>auto</code> - Header (fixed height)</li>
							<li><code>1fr</code> - Scroll area (fills remaining space)</li>
							<li><code>auto</code> - Footer (fixed height)</li>
						</ul>
					</section>

					<section>
						<h3>Sample Content</h3>
						<p>Scroll down to see more content. Notice how the header and footer stay in place while only this middle section scrolls.</p>
					</section>

					<section>
						<h3>More Content</h3>
						<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.</p>
					</section>

					<section>
						<h3>Even More Content</h3>
						<p>Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum.</p>
					</section>

					<section>
						<h3>Keep Scrolling</h3>
						<p>Sed ut perspiciatis unde omnis iste natus error sit voluptatem accusantium doloremque laudantium, totam rem aperiam, eaque ipsa quae ab illo inventore veritatis et quasi architecto beatae vitae dicta sunt explicabo.</p>
					</section>

					<section>
						<h3>Almost There</h3>
						<p>Nemo enim ipsam voluptatem quia voluptas sit aspernatur aut odit aut fugit, sed quia consequuntur magni dolores eos qui ratione voluptatem sequi nesciunt.</p>
					</section>

					<section>
						<h3>Final Section</h3>
						<p>Neque porro quisquam est, qui dolorem ipsum quia dolor sit amet, consectetur, adipisci velit, sed quia non numquam eius modi tempora incidunt ut labore et dolore magnam aliquam quaerat voluptatem.</p>
					</section>
				</div>
			</div>

			<footer class="footer">
				<p>footer</p>
			</footer>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	body {
		margin: 0;
		padding: 0;
	}

	.scroll-sandwich {
		display: grid;
		height: 100vh;
		grid-template-rows: auto 1fr auto;
	}

	.header {
		background: var(--color-bg-secondary, #f5f5f5);
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border, #e0e0e0);
		padding: 2rem;
	}

	.header h1 {
		margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
		font-size: 2rem;
	}

	.header p {
		margin: 0;
		color: var(--color-text-secondary, #666);
	}

	.scroll-area {
		overflow-y: scroll;
		background: var(--color-bg, #ffffff);
	}

	.content {
		padding: 2rem;
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.content section {
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.content h2 {
		margin-top: 0;
		font-size: 1.75rem;
	}

	.content h3 {
		margin-top: 0;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
	}

	.content ul {
		line-height: 1.8;
	}

	.content code {
		background: var(--color-bg-secondary, #f5f5f5);
		padding: 0.2rem 0.4rem;
		border-radius: 3px;
		font-size: 0.9em;
	}

	.footer {
		background: var(--color-bg-secondary, #f5f5f5);
		border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border, #e0e0e0);
		padding: 2rem;
	}

	.footer p {
		margin: 0.5rem 0;
		color: var(--color-text-secondary, #666);
	}

	/* Dark mode support */
	@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
		.scroll-sandwich {
			--color-bg: #1a1a1a;
			--color-bg-secondary: #2a2a2a;
			--color-text: #e0e0e0;
			--color-text-secondary: #999;
			--color-border: #404040;
		}
	}

	/* Scroll fog effect */
	@supports (animation-timeline: scroll()) {
		:root {
			--scroll-fog-size: 120;
		}
		.scroll-fog {
			animation:
				mask-up both linear,
				mask-down both linear;
			animation-timeline: scroll(self);
			animation-range:
				0 calc(var(--scroll-fog-size) * 1px),
				calc(100% - (var(--scroll-fog-size) * 1px)) 100%;
			mask:
				linear-gradient(white, transparent) 0 0 / 100% 0 no-repeat,
				linear-gradient(white, white) 0 50% / 100% 100% no-repeat,
				linear-gradient(transparent, white) 0 100% / 100%
					calc(var(--scroll-fog-size) * 1px) no-repeat;
			mask-composite: exclude;
		}

		@keyframes mask-up {
			to {
				mask-size:
					100% calc(var(--scroll-fog-size) * 1px),
					100% 100%;
			}
		}

		@keyframes mask-down {
			100% {
				mask-size:
					100% calc(var(--scroll-fog-size) * 1px),
					100% 100%,
					100% 0;
			}
		}
	}
</style>